      <title>德国商业活动在选举前趋于稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-24/germany-business-activity-stabilizes-ahead-of-election-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国私营部门活动在经历了六个月的下滑后于 1 月份趋于稳定，这一意外改善将受到下个月提前选举前政界人士的欢迎。经济学家曾预计该指标将继续指向活动萎缩。彭博社的 Jana Randow 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-24/germany-business-activity-stabilizes-ahead-of-election-video</guid>
